1234
01:38:19,909 --> 01:38:23,059
Does he work for me?
I mean, have you seen him before?

1235
01:38:23,163 --> 01:38:25,906
Name's Nick.
Something like that.

1236
01:38:27,951 --> 01:38:29,825
Why's he looking at me?

1237
01:38:31,955 --> 01:38:34,031
