160 feet long with four engine housings.

1388
01:52:41,978 --> 01:52:45,377
Double that, and you've got
some idea of the wing spread.

1389
01:52:45,482 --> 01:52:49,637
An airplane that challenges
a mountain for sheer size.

1390
01:52:56,401 --> 01:52:58,721
